payload.description: A web application that uses Tax Act API to gather data and uses various algorithms and statistical regression to analyze and predict the data. This application also analyses the trends in the data and creates graphs so that the users can visualize the data. Our application also has an additional feature that predicts the amount of Tax Refund a person gets based on analyzing similar data sets.
